<item>
            <title>[FLINK-15157] Make ScalaShell ensureYarnConfig() and fetchConnectionInfo() public</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-15157</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This allows users of the Scala Shell, such as Zeppelin to work better with the shell.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="13273368">FLINK-15157</key>
            <summary>Make ScalaShell ensureYarnConfig() and fetchConnectionInfo() public</summary>
                <type id="1" iconUrl="https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/viewavatar?size=xsmall&amp;avatarId=21133&amp;avatarType=issuetype">Bug</type>
